Title: [ANN][ICO] MediBloc - Health on the Blockchain! Healthcare Experience Reinvented
Body: [NEWS] Forbes announces MediBloc as the one of top crypto startups to watch in 2019  Forbes shortlisted top crypto startups to watch in 2019. Among these startups, MediBloc is highlighted as one of the most promising startups in the field of blockchain technology. Forbes described MediBloc as below.  "MediBloc tackles the endemic problem of centralized electronic health record data storage by transferring data sovereignty back to the individual. MediBloc is a decentralized, open-source blockchain healthcare data platform designed to give full ownership of personal data to patients with permissioned access control and an opportunity to monetize their data. As part of the MediBloc ecosystem, participants such as medical institutions, research organizations, insurers, and healthcare providers can all benefit through a secure and transparent exchange of data. MediBloc intends to shift the medical data paradigm to a patient-centric approach by building a medical information economic ecosystem with consumers at its core and ability for medical services to be built on top of the platform.â€  We hope you guys are super excited about MediBloc being recognized as one of the worldâ€™s top crypto startups! Title: [ANN][ICO] MediBloc - Health on the Blockchain! Healthcare Experience Reinvented
Body: [ANN] MediBloc Partners with Deloitte    On May 11, MediBloc and Deloitte Anjin LLC signed a strategic partnership agreement to reinforce blockchain-based businesses and technology.  Deloitte, a global leader in the field of accounting and consulting, has formed a startup consulting group in Korea last year and plans to develop and support promising blockchain startups. Through this business and tech partnership with MediBloc, a leading company in the blockchain field, Deloitte aims to assess the blockchain market and build a successful case of blockchain-based projects.  Dr. Wookyun Kho, CEO and co-founder of MediBloc, said, â€œWe will strive to achieve synergies that create best practices for blockchain-based business. This partnership will be an opportunity to increase the competitiveness of the blockchain business of both MediBloc and Deloitte.â€  Kim Yuseok, Director of Deloitte and group leader of Deloitte Startup Advisory Group, said, â€œCollaboration between leading companies in the blockchain industry is a must, and we expect to strengthen our competitiveness for the blockchain technology and ICO.â€  Representatives of the two companies stated that they would jointly explore and collaborate on blockchain business opportunities, and actively communicate on the market and global technology trends.  Deloitte has opened Blockchain Lab in Dublin, New York, and Hong Kong since 2016 and developed and commercialized 30+ blockchain prototypes with over 800 experts and 100 in-house developers. Deloitte offers a full range of services regarding blockchain, cryptocurrency, and ICO.  Deloitte Anjin LLC has officially launched Deloitte Startup Advisory Group last year and has been supporting startups and large corporations using Deloitteâ€™s global network.  https://medium.com/medibloc/ann-medibloc-partners-with-deloitte-410ee18a4311

Author: Artemsv
Title: [ANN][ICO] MediBloc - Health on the Blockchain! Healthcare Experience Reinvented
Body: [ANN] MediBloc to build its own blockchain platform and conduct 1:1 AIRDROP of ERC20 token! https://medium.com/medibloc/ann-medibloc-to-build-its-own-blockchain-platform-and-conduct-1-1-airdrop-of-erc20-token-baf65b539c6b  Weâ€™re excited to announce the development of our own blockchain platform as well as the issuance of ERC20 token.  Since the very beginning of MediBloc project, our team has put our utmost effort into studying the blockchain technology as well as medical record system, and have concluded that building our own blockchain platform that is specifically designed for personal health record management was inevitable.  We had initially thought that building MediBloc platform as a Dapp using EVM (Ethereum Virtual Machine) will be most cost-efficient and most effective in securing scalability and trust as EVM is most widely used for smart contract development. We came to a conclusion, however, that MediBlocâ€™s own blockchain platform will serve as a foundation for us to establish more efficient and solid security system of personal health records. We firmly believe having the complete control over blockchain core and MediBloc service will give us an ability to adapt and improve our product better and faster than any other projects according to market needs, where the market trends and the technology itself are ever-changing. We also expect to have the benefits of flexibility when expanding to other platforms by having our own blockchain platform.

Title: [ANN][ICO] MediBloc - Health on the Blockchain! Healthcare Experience Reinvented
Body: [ANN] MediBloc Partners with Hanyang University Medical Center https://medium.com/medibloc/medibloc-partners-with-hanyang-university-medical-center-e3ca9a105529    MediBloc has signed a strategic partnership agreement on April 9th with Hanyang University Medical Center, one of the nationâ€™s leading medical institutions. This is the third partnership announcement following the agreements between Oracle Medical Group (November 20th, 2017) and Kyung Hee University Dental Hospital (January 18th, 2018).  At the ceremony, both parties stated that they would work towards the same goal of building a blockchain-based PHR platform and that the hospital would give full support to its development.  â€œAs a partner, we will carry out comprehensive discussions for our platform development,â€ said Eunsol Lee, co-founder of MediBloc. He added, â€œWe will start with providing PHR platform and expand to integrating all services of MediBloc with Hanyang University Medical Centerâ€™s system. Both patients and doctors will find the integrated system very convenient and efficient.â€  Hanyang University Medical Center was established in 1972 as the largest hospital in Asia to nurture health professionals who will contribute to the improvement of public health. It is one of the most prestigious medical institutions in Korea.  Kyung-heon Kim, director of the medical center, said, â€œWe expect to advance the worldâ€™s health information system to the next level through MediBlocâ€™s blockchain-based PHR platform.â€  All participants, including healthcare professionals and patients that compose MediBloc health information ecosystem, are expected to enjoy expanded benefits from this partnership. Through this partnership agreement, MediBloc has once again proved its high practicality and achieved an opportunity to grow its business in the future.

Title: [ANN][ICO] MediBloc - Health on the Blockchain! Healthcare Experience Reinvented
Body: I still believe in this project. It is undervalued. Although I bought their coins at 0,18$ and I am always in red, there is plenty space for partnerships and real progress. Korean team of project I believe is disciplined and hard working. We have to wait more, because health and in general medical sector is now very competitive with many upcoming projects at this time we are talking. Maybe the team has to pay better attention in promotion and marketing. In the European area (at least here in Greece) people are not aware of it and some they don't understand the whole concept. How could be implemented as a real life project and how for example their medical data privacy is guaranteed. Lets give to the team some more time to prove their work and be optimists. At the end of 2018 I hope the price will be 0,50$.

Author: Jekwizor
Title: [ANN][ICO] MediBloc - Health on the Blockchain! Healthcare Experience Reinvented
Body: [ANN] 2 Billion unsold MED token is BURNT today  MediBloc, patient-centric healthcare information platform, had successfully ended its token sale on Dec 15 2017, surpassing our soft cap.  MediBloc team had decided to burn unsold tokens in order to solidify the foundation of our project and protect the interest of token sale participants. The exact amount of unsold MED token was 2,033,615,900 MED, roughly around 20% of total MED supply. As of 4pm January 20th, 2018 (Korea time), the unsold MED token has been BURNT as announced before.  There will be no return once we burn all remaining tokens, so the team at MediBloc was extra cautious in this process. Author: ggomma
Title: [ANN][ICO] MediBloc - Health on the Blockchain! Healthcare Experience Reinvented
Body: Simply speaking, MediBloc service consists of 2 main algorithms.  MediBloc's blockchain only contains data's header value. And using this(blockchain data), you can access your database.  Database's base technology is IPFS which is also distributed storage technology being used worldwide.  Briefly [Data Header Blockchain] + [Distributed Database]

Author: ggomma
Title: [ANN][ICO] MediBloc - Health on the Blockchain! Healthcare Experience Reinvented
Body: For example, Let's pretend that you have a lung cancer, you need to get an X-ray examination.  First, you went to Hospital A and had an X-ray. After seeing the x-ray data, a doctor said you need to go to Hospital B. If you go to hospital B, they possibly ask you to bring an X-ray data from hospital A or to take another same x-ray examination. That's a huge waste of resources.  MediBloc can solve these kinds of problems. You can access your medical data whenever and wherever. Before you go to the hospital, they already can have reviewed your data.

Author: MediBloc
Title: [ANN][ICO] MediBloc - Health on the Blockchain! Healthcare Experience Reinvented
Body: MediBlocâ€™s Medi Token (MED) will be listed on at least two cryptocurrency exchanges: CoinRail and BITTHAI. CoinRail is a recently launched exchange based in Korea. It is founded by world-class developers and thus has the capability to easily and securely list with various types of alt coins. It has already onboarded 12 cryptocurrencies onto its platform with a road map to onboard additional 12 currencies within the next one month. CoinRail exchange is technically most advanced and secure in Korea and can compete with the globally known exchanges. BITTHAI is a global exchange launched in Thailand that partners with a local Thai bank with foreign exchange license. USD, THB, and CNH can all be exchanged into cryptocurrencies in BITTHAI. As BITTHAI hosts three different foreign currencies unlike any other exchanges out there, it will quickly attract new users and host high volume of cryptocurrency trading.

Author: MediBloc
Title: [ANN][ICO] MediBloc - Health on the Blockchain! Healthcare Experience Reinvented
Body: What gets recorded onto the blockchain is the hashed value of healthcare data. In other words, if healthcare data is stored in the MediBloc, the hashed value on MediBloc is saved on blockchain. This secures the integrity. Healthcare data will be stored in a distributed database outside the blockchain such as IPFS. Persoanl information and medical information is encrypted and stored using a private key, giving sole ownership and access to the individual. Therefore, we would be reducing costs by storing data outside of the blockchain.

Author: ggomma
Title: [ANN][ICO] MediBloc - Health on the Blockchain! Healthcare Experience Reinvented
Body: MediBloc answered right before.  There are two main differences between other existing projects (a widely known service in the healthcare industry) and MediBloc: 1. Others are a private blockchain that builds interoperability between hospitals. This maintains the existing system where hospitals own healthcare data. MediBloc is a public blockchain that returns ownership of medical data to the patient. 2. We provide SDK (Software Development Kits), is essentially anyone can access medical data stored on the MediBloc network with the permission of the data owner. MediBloc provides a basis for a diverse future for medical services  Furthermore, both of the co-founders of MediBloc have engineering and medical backgrounds. This gives them an advantage in grasping trends and direction that the healthcare system is headed, and also quickly understanding the direction blockchain technology/ industry is headed.

Title: [ANN][ICO] MediBloc - Health on the Blockchain! Healthcare Experience Reinvented
Body: [ANN][ICO] MediBloc - Health on the Blockchain! Healthcare Experience ReinventedğŸ™ŒğŸ»  Blockchain based Healthcare Information Ecosystem  MediBloc is a decentralized healthcare information ecosystem for patients, healthcare providers and data researchers, built on blockchain technology.  Digital Healthcare Wallet. Your personal healthcare information, owned by you. Every interaction with every medical professional, procedure, or pharmacy neatly organized in one place. Secured on the blockchain.  Reduce Redundancies. Data interoperability through MediBloc brings complete patient health autonomy: helping doctors provide better care, better diagnosis and ultimately a better, more personalized healthcare experience.  Real Time Patient Database Bring unparalleled healthcare data samples from a global pool of every region and demographics: eliminate location bias and increase sample size to accelerate the advancement of medicine faster than ever.  A Platform with Unlimited Potential MediBloc provides data I/O control(core) and interfaces(service) for 3rd party applications & services. On top of MediBloc platform, all kinds of services using medical data can be implemented.
